title: Jay Laga’aia appears on I'm A Celebrity after being booted | Daily Mail Online
text: Share 114 shares Another viewer called @trevorgerdes questioned, '@ImACelebrityAU how is that #celebJay is on the TV in tonight's show when he was voted out last Sunday'. 'Who's the bloke singing in the background of the darts game? Was that Jay??? #ImACelebrityAU' asked Twitter user @AnouskaHaaket. The camera then panned to guest Carson Kressley, whose stint on the show began on Monday, looking on as Kris and Tziporah got into it. Isnt he out? Jay was seen laying back on his camp bed and strumming his ukulele as Tziporah Malkah and Kris Smith argued in the foreground Viewers noticed: Twitter user @RowanBrookes wrote: '@ImACelebrityAU just played footage of Tziporah and Kris arguing...But Jay was in the background? He got booted on Sunday?'\ Daily Mail Australia has reached out to Channel Ten for comment. It's unclear if the mystery appearance was an editing error, however a similar hiccup happened last year's season of The Bachelorette starring Georgia Love. During the first cocktail party, a mysterious blonde female dressed in a plain white blouse was seen lurking in the background. They noticed! The show's fans took to Twitter to point out the strange moment The woman was then seen strolling through directly in front of the camera while Georgia chatted away with the boys. Meanwhile, 53-year-old Jay left South Africa 13.1kg lighter, having lived on mostly beans and rice during his three-week stay in the jungle. Speaking in his exit interview, the visibly emotional actor revealed his eight children were the motivation for his transformation. Blooper: It's unclear if the mystery appearance was an editing error, however a similar hiccup happened last year's season of The Bachelorette starring Georgia Love Scene stealer: During the first cocktail party, a mysterious blonde female dressed in a plain white blouse was seen lurking in the background 'If they become huge, that's my fault and my wife has always said that,' an in inspired Jay revealed. The singer said his health had improved since entering the jungle and that is, 'great for me, but I've got to do this to not only change mine but my kids' lives as well.' Slimmer!
